data.title: Jonas Brothers and Camp Rock Cast
data.meta_description:
CAMP ROCK - The "Camp Rock" cast comes together for the special hosted premiere weekend of Disney Channel's next original movie musical "Camp Rock," as part of the Disney Channel Original Movie franchise premiering FRIDAY, JUNE 20 (8:00 P.M., ET/PT) on Disney Channel. (DISNEY CHANNEL/ADAM LARKEY)
	KEVIN JONAS, NICK JONAS, DEMI LOVATO, JOE JONAS, MEAGHAN JETTE MARTIN, ALYSON STONER, ANNA MARIA PEREZ DE TAGLE
